OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIncreasingly
OL,6,Fcloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight, with outbreaks of light
OL,8,Frain possible during the early hours.
OL,9,FBreezy, especially near coasts and
OL,10,Fhills. Mild overnight temperatures.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA largely cloudy start,
OL,13,Fespecially across western hills.
OL,14,FTurning bright, with some sunny spells
OL,15,Flater in the day. Winds easing. Warm
OL,16,For very warm temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
